Rating: 3
A great basic recipe. I also made it with peeled, pitted fresh peaches instead of strawberries - fabulous. Then I tried fresh blueberries. It would be good with any fresh seasonal fruit - but you would have to strain berries for seeds. Not like an ice cream - more like a sherbet. Okay to use low fat buttermilk.

